Executive Profile
John Prentiss Bartlett CFAPortfolio Manager, ETFis Series Trust I - Reaves Utilities ETFAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships----
Background

		Mr. John Prentiss Bartlett, CFA is a Vice President, Portfolio Manager, and Electric Utility Analyst at W. H. Reaves & Co., Inc., and was previously a Performance Analyst since 1995. Mr. Bartlett specializes in the equity analysis of electric utilities and industrial companies. He is a Chartered Financial Analyst. Mr. Bartlett holds a B.A. from Connecticut College.	
	



Corporate Headquarters
10 Exchange PlaceJersey City, New Jersey 07302United StatesPhone: 800-975-8395Fax: 201-332-8593
Board Members Memberships
Vice President of W H Reaves & Co Inc and Director of W H Reaves & Co IncThe Advisors' Inner Circle Fund II - Reaves Utilities and Energy Infrastructure Fund
Education
BA Connecticut College
Other Affiliations
